== Salad

=== Into
Helps you to manage your applications and features.


Salad will help you to create new project and migrate features and stories from previously created project. You will also be able to create stories and share them across projects, allowing you to quickly build scenarios.

Future releases of Salad will allow you to share scenarios with colleagues and friends.

Salad is a simple application that allow users to manage their projects & their feature, inspired by Cucumber, Salad allows you to create projects and associate features with them.

== Features
Create projects
Create & manage project features 
Create stories for features

== Future features
In future releases, users will be able to link these features with LightHouse milestones & export features into Cucumber features & steps.